      public LevelSetScreen()

  • Method Details

    • setChoosingEffect

      private void setChoosingEffect​(javafx.scene.image.ImageView imageView, javafx.scene.text.Text setNameText, java.lang.String setName)
      This is a reusable method to help LevelSetScreen to set up interactive animation effect when user hover the mouse on a set represented by a crate.
      Parameters:
      imageView - ImageView which to play the animation on.
      setNameText - Text to show the name of set.
      setName - String value specifying the name of set to be shown on the given Text.
